WEBVTT

00:00,000 --> 00:04,950
When most output rises but outcomes stay flat, decision rhythm is usually the bottleneck.

00:05,000 --> 00:09,950
Without a clear review habit, gamification quality drifts even when effort increases.

00:10,000 --> 00:14,950
Assign one owner, track one metric, and review one live decision every week.

00:15,000 --> 00:19,950
Prototype quickly, test in live work for one week, and log evidence before scaling.

00:20,000 --> 00:24,950
Teams get better adoption, cleaner decisions in review, and fewer repeat corrections in delivery.

00:25,000 --> 00:29,950
What is the first review loop you can install this week?
